## Complete System State Machine

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> VaultCreated
    
    state VaultCreated {
        [*] --> MnemonicGenerated
        MnemonicGenerated --> KeysDerived
        KeysDerived --> VaultReady
    }
    
    VaultReady --> Importing: Import provider data
    Importing --> Capturing: Active capture running
    
    state Capturing {
        [*] --> StreamActive
        StreamActive --> ACUProcessing
        ACUProcessing --> Classified
        Classified --> Stored
    }
    
    Stored --> Searching: User searches
    Searching --> ContextAssembled: AI assistant query
    ContextAssembled --> [*]
    
    Stored --> Listing: Sell data
    Listing --> Sold: Marketplace sale
    Sold --> [*]
    
    Stored --> Detecting: Run detection
    Detecting --> EvidenceGenerated
    EvidenceGenerated --> [*]
    
    Stored --> Syncing: Multi-device sync
    Syncing --> InSync
    InSync --> [*]
```